@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 180

actor "Nhan vien" as Staff
participant "StaffFeaturePanels.paymentPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "StaffFeatureController\n(Facade)" as Facade
participant "PaymentController" as Controller
participant "StaffService" as Service
participant "StaffBillingRepository" as Repository
participant "JpaStaffDataStore" as DataStore
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Staff, DB: QUY TRINH THU TIEN HOA DON (TIEN MAT / CHUYEN KHOAN)

Staff -> View : 1. Chon hoa don chua thu va phuong thuc thanh toan
View -> Facade : 2. markInvoicePaid(invoice, paymentMethod)
activate Facade

Facade -> Controller : 3. markInvoicePaid(invoice, paymentMethod)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 4. markInvoicePaid(invoiceId, paymentMethod)
activate Service
Service -> Repository : 5. markInvoicePaid(invoiceId, paymentMethod)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataStore : 6. markInvoicePaid(invoiceId, paymentMethod)
activate DataStore

DataStore -> DB : 7. UPDATE HOA_DON set paid=true, method, paidAt
activate DB
DB -->> DataStore : 8. Success
DataStore -->> Repository : 9. InvoiceItem da cap nhat
Repository -->> Service : 10. InvoiceItem da cap nhat
Service -->> Controller : 11. InvoiceItem da cap nhat
Controller -->> Facade : 12. Thanh toan thanh cong
Facade -->> View : 13. Hien thong bao thanh cong

deactivate DB
deactivate DataStore
deactivate Repository
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
deactivate Facade

View -> View : 14. Refresh danh sach hoa don chua thu
View -->> Staff : 15. San sang in bien lai
@enduml
